            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Catalister is an AI-powered platform for Shopify dropshippers that automates product research, generates SEO-optimized descriptions, and syncs products directly to your store. It replaces hours of manual work with automated workflows, helping sellers launch products in seconds instead of hours.",
