            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Catalister is ideal for Shopify dropshippers, small e-commerce business owners, and marketing agencies managing multiple Shopify stores. It's especially valuable for sellers who source from suppliers like AliExpress and want to automate product listing creation with AI-generated, SEO-optimized content.",
